          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Hot Takes: Golf Fashion Edition",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><em>What's In, What's Out, and What Always Works</em></p><p>Let's face it, golf fashion is having a moment. Scratch that, golf fashion is <em>the</em> moment. From fairway fits to post-round cocktails, the lines between sport and style have officially blurred. And as the game modernizes, so do the wardrobes of those who play it. Here are our unfiltered thoughts on what's trending, what's tired, and what will never go out of style.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
