    "text_2": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "What's In: Minimalism with a Statement",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Today's best looks feel effortless, even if they're meticulously styled. Think tonal layers, tailored silhouettes, and subtle prints that say more with less. Brands like <strong>Malbon</strong>, <strong>Manors</strong>, and <strong>J.Lindeberg</strong> are leading the charge. They are delivering clean lines, high performance, and just the right amount of edge.</p><p>On the accessories front, we're loving performance hats with heritage flair (shoutout <strong>G/FORE</strong> and <strong>Bogey Boys</strong>) and golf bags that double as style pieces. If it looks like it could've walked off a fashion week runway <em>and</em> walked 18 holes, it's a win.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_1",
        "text_1"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "alignment": "left",
        "enable_animation": true
      }
    },
