    "text_4": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "What's Timeless: Texture, Fit, and Confidence",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>A well-fitted polo. A lightweight merino sweater. Neutral trousers that pair with everything. Some things never miss.</p><p>No matter what trends come and go, the real key to great golf style is wearing clothes that feel good and move with you. Enter <strong>Greyson</strong>, <strong>RLX Ralph Lauren</strong>, and <strong>KJUS </strong>- brands that balance performance with polish. Texture (hello, pique cotton and brushed knits), versatility, and pieces that transition effortlessly from course to club are always a good idea.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
