    "text_5": {
      "type": "content-block",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "What to Shop Now at TRENDYGOLF",
            "tag": "h2",
            "size": "h3",
            "font": "serif"
          }
        },
        "text_1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Need to refresh your closet? Here are a few can't-miss picks:</p><ul><li><strong>Greyson polos</strong> for sleek prints that don't overwhelm</li><li><strong>J.Lindeberg trousers</strong> for modern tailoring with stretch</li><li><strong>Malbon headwear</strong> that adds personality without overdoing it</li><li><strong>G/FORE gloves and accessories</strong> for that elevated detail work</li></ul><p>Golf fashion is evolving and your closet should, too. Whether you're a minimalist purist or looking to turn heads on every tee box, we've got the fit for you.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
